          <p
            class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-blue-300 font-semibold mb-6 leading-snug drop-shadow-lg"
          >
            Electrical & Electronics Engineer | IoT Engineer @ sensors.AFRICA <span
              class="text-blue-400">#CodeForAfrica</span
            > | Full Stack Web Developer | <span class="text-green-400"
              >Hydroponic Tech Enthusiast</span
            >
